      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "Salt and Pepper",
      "notes": "to taste"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your air fryer to 350\u00b0F (175\u00b0C).",
    "Cut the bell peppers, red onions, cucumbers into thin slices.",
    "Slice radishes thinly. Combine all vegetables in a large bowl.",
    "Add lemon juice and apple cider vinegar, mix well with salt and pepper for taste.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over vegetables and toss to coat evenly.",
    "Transfer the mixture into the air fryer basket and cook for 10-12 minutes or until crispy.",
    "Serve immediately."
